(109130, 'Roots rebellion', 'http://www.indievox.com/obrothaz', 'http://cdn2-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/120000/109130/pix/109130180X180.jpg?1427805304', 27, 'Out of the most unlikely places Roots Rebellion was born, bringing the musical rebellion\r\nto the island nation of Taiwan and then to the world.  Forged together by their love of music the members of Roots Rebellion come from all different places, Trinidad and Tobago, Jamaica, USA, France, Belize and Taiwan.  The musical vibes consists of the real roots reggae vibes that will keep your body moving through the night.  The band has powerful vocalists up with seasoned soulful singer Sherwyne Splenda and newcomer Sunny Smalls singing in both English, Mandarin and Taiwanese.\r\n在一個完全對雷鬼音樂陌生的台灣，正有一群對雷鬼音樂有熱情的朋友們組了個\r\n純雷鬼樂團，將為台灣帶來新的音樂叛亂，然後到世界。Roots Rebellion的團員來自不同的地方，特立尼達和多巴哥，牙買加，美國，法國，貝里斯和台灣，大家對音樂的熱愛，產生了雷鬼音樂共鳴，不自覺聽了，身體也隨著那感覺擺動著。歌手的實力生非常有爆發力和音樂上的才華，經驗非常豐富的深情歌手Sherwyne Splenda帶出新一輩歌手來自台灣Sunny Smalls，融入了國語，台語，英語的表演風格，是一個非常有實力的團體。\r\n\r\n'),
