(148022, 'Love Da Music Taiwan', 'http://www.indievox.com/lovedamusictaiwan', 'http://cdn-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/150000/148022/pix/148022180X180.jpg?1427774013', 19, '最愛音樂 Love Da Music創業逾十四年，在業界一直建立良好聲譽，是目前東南亞具規模的唱片／音樂發行商之一。Love Da Music代理全球超過一百五十個獨立音樂品牌的出品，當中包括V2/Coop、Play It Again Sam、Warp、Ninja Tunes、Sub Pop、Wall of Sound、!K7、Kitsuné、Om Records、Infectious、Ministry of Sound、Hotel Costes、Naïve、摩登天空等知名品牌，而這名單會不斷伸延下去。\r\n\r\n我們不會拘泥於任何音樂類型，也不會固步自封，我們為Love Da Music今天在東南亞地區所取得的成績感到自豪。我們必能讓喜歡音樂的你找到你的「最愛音樂」，當然這一切取決於 “How Deep Is Your Love?”\r\n\r\n自2011年開始，最愛音樂與百代音樂結盟，將各大獨立廠牌的音樂在台灣推廣，已為台灣的獨立音樂市場開啟了新的面貌。除了持續為聽眾帶來最具品味與特色的音樂外，也計劃安排歐美藝人樂團來台演出，並與在地品牌合作，創造更多音樂的可能性。'),
(148140, '台北爵士大樂團', 'http://www.indievox.com/tjo', 'http://cdn3-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/150000/148140/pix/148140180X180.jpg?1427774016', 7, '台北爵士大樂團Taipei Jazz Orchestra於2009年成立，由爵士音樂家李承育擔任指揮，成員則結合了國內最優秀、最活躍的爵士及古典樂手。此張專輯由DOWNBEAT爵士名人堂Gene Aitken擔任製作人、葛萊美獎錄音師Jim Linahon擔任錄音師，並邀請優質女聲方雅賢重新演繹納京高Orange Coloured Sky、木匠兄妹 Sing, Sing a Song經典樂曲。\r\n更多關於台北爵士大樂團的訊息，請上www.tjo.com.tw。\r\n\r\n★台北爵士大樂團Taipei Jazz Orchestra★ \r\n【團長Director】侯宇彪 Yui-Biau Hou\r\n【音樂總監Music Supervisor】Gene Aitken\r\n【指揮Conductor】李承育Cheng-Yu Lee\r\n【薩克斯風Saxophone】楊曉恩Shawna Yang, 李政修Cheng-Hsiu Lee,張坤德Kunter Chang,周泰明Terry Chou,吳志桓Chih-Huan Wu\r\n【長號Trombone】Nick Javier, 梁兆豐 Jeffrey Liang,	謝蓉慧Jung-Hui Hsieh,李建緯Jerry Lee \r\n【小號Trumpet】鄭文鳳Antonio Cheng, Adam MacBlan, 莊婷湄Ting-Mei Chuang, 古嘉訢Chia-Hsing Ku, 廖冠堯Yao Liao\r\n【吉他Guitar】黃俊仁Paco Huang\r\n【低音提琴Bass】池田欣彌IKEDA Kinya\r\n【鋼琴Piano】烏野薰Kaoru Uno\r\n【鼓組Drums】吳純瑩Brandy Wu'),
(148203, 'Fad', 'http://www.indievox.com/fad', 'http://cdn1-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/150000/148203/pix/148203180X180.jpg?1427774017', 5, 'Fad的音樂，大概是以英倫色彩為基調，再拼疊上不同質感的材料而成。\n\n我們忠於樂隊名字的意思，任性探索另的角度、別的感覺，試圖移動基調本身。\n \n2012年夏，十號風球韋森特襲港，我們逆著風傻著陸台北作小型巡演。\n\n2014年春，首張專輯《Fad》誕生，將多年來的作品沈澱於激光中，為過去旋轉出一個總結。專輯發佈派對《Playground is Fad》，大體的裝置式佈置，小巧的音樂蛋紀念品，在火炭藝術磁場中一個暗具個性的Café裡，釋放一夜遊樂。\n\n同年初夏，第二個MV《Dream in Dream》實現，一個想入非非非份之想的超現實夢裡夢。http://youtu.be/KZifsiuIrB0 \n\n夢更有幸發到日本獨立音樂網http://www.indienative.com/2014/05/526418/ \n \nFad成員現有Sky (主唱及結他)、Sammy (結他)、Carina (低音結他)、雪 (鍵琴及和唱) 和 Baller (鼓)。\n\nFad plays music mostly influenced in Brit Rock, together with different elements and textures. \n\nWe followed our band name, thinking beyond another horizon, another feeling, to move with our instincts. \n\nSummer 2012, Severe Typhoon Vicente brought Hurricane \n\nSignal No. 10 to Hong Kong, we brought our music tour to Taiwan.\n\nSpring 2014, we released our self-titled album 《Fad》, compiling our music throughout the years into it. Our album release party 《Playground is Fad》has been held in a stylish café in Fotan with different large installations while giving out small gifts music eggs to our audience. \n\nIn early summer 2014, we have published our second MV 《Dream in Dream》, bringing you into a fantastic dream. http://youtu.be/KZifsiuIrB0 \n\nThe dream has been spread out to Japan indie music web http://www.indienative.com/2014/05/526418/\n\nFad is now a combination of vocalist Sky Donkey, guitarist Sammy Circle, bassist Carina River, keyboardist Snow Piece and drummer Baller Dust.\n\nFad – Sofia MV \nhttp://youtu.be/diZ09Jxr93g \n\nDiscography:\n1.       Oh so...! Compilation\nPublisher: Pin Up Music \nPublishing Year: 2011\nArtist: Various Artists \nMusic Style: Pop, Brit-pop, Rock, Rap/Hip Hop, Dance\nPrice: Free\nDownload Link: \nhttp://www.imusicbox.hk/digital_desc.php?show_cate=0&p_autono=199\n\n2.       Underground Compilation CD4\nRecord Label: The Underground\nPublishing Year: 2011\nArtist: Various Bands \nGenre: Rock, Punk-Pop\nDescription: Eleven Hong Kong bands from modern folk to melding jazz \npiano rock thrown in with some blues-based rock, a sprinkling of \nelectronica & culminating in party-rock!\nPrice: Buy CD - US$12.97; Download Album (MP3) - US$9.99\n      9. Salamander - FAD (Buy separate track - US $0.99)\n      10. So Tired - FAD (Buy separate track - US $0.99)\nAlbum Details: \nhttp://www.cdbaby.com/cd/undergroundmusic3\nYou may preview songs before buying the album, support local music!\n \n3.       Be A Phonograph - Phonograph Compilation CD\nPublishing Year: 2012\nArtist: Fad, Hence N Comma, Sadness Oyster, Self, The Smooth Jelly Club\nGenre: Britrock, Electronica, Post Rock\nDescription: Five Hong Kong bands who are great fans of the unique and \nfashionable bar in Hong Kong Tsimshatsui – Phonograph, get together and\nrecorded a compilation CD to commemorate the bar. The bar has closed \ndown in April 2012, and will move on to a new place soon.\nPrice: Buy CD – HK$40\n           2. Fad – As Great As Those Great Volkswagon Ads\n           7. Fad – So Tired\nPlease contact us if you would like to buy the album, thank you!\n\n4. Fad Demo CD\n    Publishing Year: 2012\n    Artist: Fad\n       1. Sofia\n       2. Starry Memory\n       3. As Great As Those Great Volkswagon Ads\n       4. So Tired\n\n       Bonus Tracks:\n       5. Salamander\n       6. Dream in Dream\n\n\n4. Fad – Fad\nPublishing Year: 2014\nArtist: Fad\nGenre: Brit rock, Indie rock\nDescription: Self-titled debut album. British. Faddish. Alternative. Naive. Taste like a cream tea, bittersweet but not a symphony.\n\nPhysical direct mail order: http://goo.gl/3TZSuk \n\nDownload of our album 《Fad》digital version:-\nhttp://fadhkband.bandcamp.com/album/fad \n\nPurchase also available at Tom Lee TST, White Noise and Zoo Records\n'),
(148223, 'Dihang ', 'http://www.indievox.com/dihang', 'http://cdn1-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/150000/148223/pix/148223180X180.jpg?1427774018', 1, '我是Dihang，我的音樂，我的生活\n喜歡在有靈感有時間的時候，錄音自己寫的歌\n因為每一首歌都是生活的寫照，都是活著的記錄\n\n花蓮縣阿美族人\n在教會長大從小接觸音樂，卻看不懂譜\n有個出名的親戚叫檳榔兄弟\n正職是鼓手，不過最近漸漸開始變成吉他手\n國小學過鋼琴，不過通通還給老師了，現在是自由發揮\n\nMy blogspot: http://dihangs.blogspot.tw/'),
