(216675, 'Interpretaciones del leve sentir ', 'http://www.indievox.com/lasideasfugazes', 'http://cdn1-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/240000/216675/pix/216675180X180.jpg?1427775545', 0, 'Interpretaciones del leve sentir (a.k.a. Idls) started as a series of experimental home recordings trying to show feelings, mental dialogues and express inner ideas through music. Idls is nowadays a hybrid of electronic music (IDM influenced) and pure/human sounds started out in the own body, in guitars or even in some ethnic instruments (Folk influenced). Idls is probably an endless quest through the emotions and wishes.'),
