(9852, 'Sons of Homer', 'http://www.indievox.com/sonsofhomer', 'http://cdn2-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/30000/9852/pix/9852180X180.jpg?1427770964', 0, 'The Beatles, The Rolling Stones, Led Zeppelin, Culture Club, that hot lesbian duo from Russia….all amazing bands in their own right but one band in particular is considered by many to be one of the best bands ever. The problem is…….the world has yet to hear them.\r\n\r\nThey are a band unlike any you have seen. They are humorous, extremely talented, and always aiming to please. They write all of their own original tracks which target all genres from rock, reggae, funk, soul, country and R n’ B – music that makes you want to dance. They have been praised as saviors of rock in Taiwan and proprietors of the art form of performance and entertainment. A Sons of Homer show is exciting, rocking and most of all – unforgettable.'),
