(10369, 'Brand New Sin', 'http://www.indievox.com/brandnewsin', 'http://cdn2-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/30000/10369/pix/10369180X180.jpg?1427770975', 1, '關於Brand New Sin的故事可要回溯到2002年，該團透過Now Or Never Records發行的首張同名專輯「Brand New Sin」，便展現了Brand New Sin(以下簡稱B.N.S.)天生優異的資質、熟捻的技巧以及對於音樂的熱情與硬漢般的態度，綜合成為一股無可否認的生猛搖滾本質，並將B.N.S.推向搖滾樂界的明日之星!! 主唱Joe Altier顆粒明顯的硬漢嗓音搭上紮實的搖滾節奏，令人震驚的出色雙吉他獨奏，遵循著南方藍調搖滾的路線!! 2003年的demo，馬上就被Century Media Records鎖定，於該旗下發行的作品「Recipe For Disaster」，B.N.S.瞬間成為聚焦之的，受到Billboard與Entertainment Weekly大力讚揚，成為Guitar One與Guitar World上不可忽視之樂團，近期更為WWE摔角巨星Big Show製作出場主題曲&quot;Crank It Up&quot;!! 為其硬漢形象大力背書!! \r\n   B.N.S.集Motorhead、Guns N'' Roses、Pantera、Metallica各家精華，灑上Lynyrd Skynyrd的南方憂鬱調味，&quot;永不妥協也不受時光腐蝕的搖滾原力&quot;，Joe Altier說出了B.N.S.的音樂本質!! 最新作品「Tequila」又再次呈現出B.N.S.出色的搖滾原力，與Black Label Society如出一徹的硬漢作風&quot;Did Me Wrong&quot;、&quot;Spare the Agony&quot;與&quot;Motormeth&quot;，南方搖滾的大無謂態度&quot;See the Sun&quot;，Peter Steele(Type O Negative)友情助拳的&quot;Reaper Man&quot;，翻唱英倫經典老團The Animals招牌名曲&quot;House of the Rising Sun&quot;，在借酒消愁的惆悵之餘卻又有著永不妥協的硬漢精神啊!!\r\n    \r\n\r\n   BRAND NEW SIN have returned with a voracious hard rock assault laden with soaring, captivating melodies and crushing anthems that are sure to get anyone''s blood flowing and fists pumping. This highly anticipated new offering, Tequila, features an abundance of stellar guitar work from Kenny Dunham and Kris Wiechmann, who stepped up greatly to further establish themselves as one of rock''s premiere tandems. The Syracuse-based quintet have greatly evolved over the past few years, honing their musicianship to become one of the most acclaimed pure American rock acts around today. \r\n\r\nBRAND NEW SIN first burst upon the scene in 2002 with their groundbreaking self-titled Now Or Never Records debut album. The stunning debut offering was produced by local knobsman Pete Walker at Village Recorders in Liverpool, New York and was one of those rare rock records erected through sheer talent, skill, passion and an iron clad work ethic. It boasted an undeniable raw fury that quickly had critics hailing the band as the next big thing in rock. \r\n\r\nThe group went on to earn a devoted legion of fans through relentless touring with a wide array of artists, from Black Label Society and Slayer to Breaking Benjamin and Saliva. It''s the stunning blend of frontman Joe Altier''s captivating roar and melodic overtones mixed with the band''s gritty, rock-solid rhythm section, stunning dual guitar solos and pummeling hooks that helped this group standout from the pack and appeal to a diverse audience. &quot;Brand New Sin is unyielding rock n'' roll power and timelessness,&quot; says Altier, &quot;You can pick our record up 20 years from now and it will still feel as fresh and relevant as it does today.&quot; Indeed, BRAND NEW SIN forged a path to ultimately join the ranks of classic bands like AC/DC.\r\n\r\nIn 2003, BRAND NEW SIN added new drummer Kevin Dean to the fold, while longtime guitarists Kenny Dunham, Kris Wiechmann and bassist Chuck Kahl stepped up their involvement. The band ultimately grew tighter and their newfound energy was put into their songwriting for the greater half of 2004, as the band hooked back up with Walker to record their eagerly awaited sophomore offering. The early demos quickly caught the attention of Century Media Records, who immediately signed the band to a worldwide deal. \r\n\r\nThe group stormed back with the stunning Recipe For Disaster album in 2005, which immediately received critical praise from Billboard and Entertainment Weekly, while Guitar One and Guitar World both hailed them as a band to keep an eye on. Recipe For Disaster saw the group begin to find their definitive sound incorporating a variety of metal and hard rock influences ranging from Motorhead and Guns N'' Roses to Pantera and Metallica, while traces of Lynyrd Skynyrd remain evident, lending them the sort of bluesy, swampy edge they are best known for. \r\n\r\nThey proceeded to tour relentlessly with such genre titans as Black Label Society, C.O.C. and Motorhead, further solidifying their diehard fanbase as Fuse and MTV2 embraced the epic track ''Black and Blue.'' They also recently recorded a new version of the entrance theme music for Big Show, the 7-foot, 500-pound ECW wrestler. The theme, &quot;Crank It Up,&quot; was first heard on the compilation CD WWE: Wreckless Intent, which debuted at #8 on the Billboard charts. \r\n\r\nBRAND NEW SIN entered Method of Groove studios in Brooklyn with producer Joey Z (Life of Agony, Stereomud) in April of 2006 to begin tracking Tequila and emerged with an album that is sure to stand the test of time. The disc, mastered by the acclaimed George Marino (Metallica, AC/DC, Guns N'' Roses) at Sterling Sound, also features a guest vocal appearance by Peter Steele (Type O Negative) on ''Reaper Man'' and is the perfect representation of what this group is ultimately capable of creating. \r\n\r\nBRAND NEW SIN is the definition of authentic, meat-and-potatoes classic hard rock chased with hints of down home, southern style blues and an undeniable raw fury that refuses to be denied. \r\n'),
(10371, 'Cryptopsy', 'http://www.indievox.com/cryptopsy', 'http://cdn1-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/30000/10371/pix/10371180X180.jpg?1427770975', 1, '\r\n加拿大，一直以來給人慵懶愜意、民風樸實的印象，實在很難令人想像可以誕生出如此兇殘的死亡金屬樂團；成軍於1988年，創團初期以Necrosis之名闖蕩魁北克地下搖滾樂壇，其敲打著極端Death Metal音符讓樂團名聲迅速在當地音樂圈中蔓延開；由於對樂手技巧要求甚高，成員變動非常頻繁，最後在瘋狂主唱Lord Worm、鼓手Flo Mounier和吉他手Alex Auburn三位軸心人物先後加入之下，總算替樂團找到明確的創作方向。\r\n\r\n93年自製發表Demo並正式改名為Cryptopsy，隔年隨即加盟獨立廠牌發表首張正式專輯「Blasphemy Made Flesh」，可惜並未引起迴響，直到96年關鍵性的一擊「None So Vile」才讓Cryptopsy真正嚐到成功的滋味；每首歌編曲縝密、複雜又具有深度，就像是一幅結合殘暴與柔美的藝術品；尤其Flo那屌到不像話的超絕鼓技實在令人張目結舌，「None So Vile」理所當然成為樂迷爭相收藏的死亡金屬極經典，也為Cryptopsy贏得一只國際名廠Century Media的合約；就在樂團蓄勢待發，準備大舉進攻國際舞台之同時，Lord Worm表示要離開樂團從事教育工作，主唱部份則改由嗓音偏向Hardcore味道的Mike DiSalvo入替；接下來陸續發表加入旋律色彩以及前衛樂句的「Whisper Supremacy」、「And Then You''ll Beg」，可看出Cryptopsy不斷進步之企圖心，與相近性質的同輩樂團比較之下特顯優異！\r\n\r\n經過Lord Worm短暫回巢之作「Once Was Not」三年後，Cryptopsy首度增添由正妹Maggie Durand所擔任的鍵盤手位置，更網羅前Melodic Death/Metalcore樂團3 Mile Scream的Matt McGachy擔任主唱，推出第六張由團員合力製作的全新專輯「The Unspoken King」，封面散發出中古世紀邪惡帝國之氣息。Matt加入所引起的化學變化讓&quot;Worship Your Demons&quot;、&quot;The Headsmen&quot;呈現Deathcore之厚重力道，證明樂團的全新出發；充滿爵士變拍橋段&quot;Silence The Tyrants&quot;讓樂手實力完全發揮，熟練的技巧搭配絕非泛泛之輩可以比擬；千萬別被&quot;Bemoan The Martyr&quot;、&quot;The Plagued&quot;開頭Matt的順耳清腔給騙到了，隨後馬上以低沉豬吠咆哮將人抓回至混亂漩渦；Alex Auburn刀光劍影的吉他Solo在&quot;Resurgence Of An Empire&quot;中大肆宰殺，沒人能倖免；&quot;Anoint The Dead&quot;重擊程度讓人陷入抓狂情緒；最後，&quot;(Exit) The Few&quot;從開場Matt陰沉的呢喃緩緩鋪陳到最後憤慨思緒被牽動導致型成雜亂無章的群體暴亂，但隨著時間歸零，一且也將化為荒無；留下的，只有這一棟毫無生氣，陰森詭譎的死亡堡壘….'),
(10372, 'Dark Fortress', 'http://www.indievox.com/darkfortress', 'http://cdn2-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/30000/10372/pix/10372180X180.jpg?1427770975', 0, '成軍於1994年的Melodic Black Metal亡靈軍團Dark Fortress，來自以旋律/速度而盛名的金屬王朝–"德國"；但他們豪不理會主流市場之運作，以陰森氣氛營造出一首首冰冷詭譎的邪惡之作，建立起一掛極端死忠信徒，登上Summer Breeze Open Air和Kaltenbach Open Air等重金屬音樂祭典；更受到大廠欽點招攬，將Dark Fortress送上國際舞台，打造出德意志黑金屬指標。\r\n\r\n由主腦Asvargyr為首的Dark Fortress，96/97年分別自製Demo、Split開始在地下黑金屬樂壇間廣為流傳；隨即加入獨立廠牌Red Stream，發表「Tales from Eternal Dusk」以及「Profane Genocidal Creations」兩張作品，對於Dark Fortress那毫無人性的血腥作風，無疑是給了養慣順耳旋律的德國民眾一記當頭棒喝！04年轉入Black Attakk旗下推出封面由知名異類藝術家Travis Smith操刀的「Stab Wounds」；雖團員更動頻繁，主要還是以Asvargyr以及01年入團的V. Santura為創作中心。 '),
(10373, 'Dark Tranquillity', 'http://www.indievox.com/darktranquillity', 'http://cdn3-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/30000/10373/pix/10373180X180.jpg?1427770975', 4, 'Dark Tranquillity is a melodic death metal band from Gothenburg, Sweden. Starting in 1989 named Septic Broiler, they have had a fairly stable line-up from the beginning, unlike many bands in the genre. \r\n\r\nIn 1993, Anders Fridén, the original lead vocalist, left the band to join In Flames. Mikael Stanne, formerly playing rhythm guitar became the vocalist, with Fredrik Johansson taking over the guitars. Mikael also recorded vocals with In Flames. However, contrary to popular belief, he was never a full member of that band; he was a session vocalist and sang to help out the members of In Flames. \r\n\r\nIn 1998, before the release of the album Projector, Johannson left the band. Keyboardist Martin Brändström and bassist Michael Nicklasson were added to the line-up, and Martin Henriksson switched to the guitar. This album was nominated for a Swedish Grammy Award. Their next albums were Haven (2000), Damage Done (2002), Character (2005) and Fiction (2007).\r\n\r\nDark Tranquillity is known to be a pioneer of the Gothenburg Metal sound alongside bands such as At the Gates and In Flames. Anders Jivarp has been the drummer since the band was formed.\r\n');
