(64953, '少年維持的煩惱', 'http://www.indievox.com/sorrowofyouth', 'http://cdn2-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/90000/64953/pix/64953180X180.jpg?1427787373', 353, '少年維持的煩惱來自高雄，成立於2009年12月底，團員分別是胡俊(主唱，吉他)，葉子樵(吉他，合成器)，李侹毅(貝斯，合音)，以及胡偉(鼓，打擊樂器)。曲風有別於一般南台灣風行的龐克/金屬樂隊，演奏的是新興的後龐克復興，結合台語歌詞，加強主唱胡俊所想要表達之強烈在地歸屬感。少年維持的煩惱於2012年春天發表第一張錄音室EP “城市躁動"。\n\n\nSorrow of youth are a Taiwanese indie-pop band based in Kaohsiung, Taiwan, who formed in 2009. The band consists of Chun "Sib" Hu( lead vocals, guitar), Edison Yeh( lead guitar, synth), Ting-yi "Mark" Li( backing vocals, bass), and Wei "Wayne" Hu( drum, percussion). They made a debut on 2, July, in LivingRoom live house, Kaohsiung. The first studio EP "Frisky Town" is now released.'),
