(75393, 'START OF THE DAY', 'http://www.indievox.com/startoftheday', 'http://cdn1-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/90000/75393/pix/75393180X180.jpg?1427792399', 268, '「望向無邊際的海岸,爬上往天空那段閃閃發亮的階梯, 從那裡所看到的景色,是多麼溫柔且深刻。 因此,我們揮舞著指揮棒,將旋律與意念不斷交疊。」\n從日本來的female-fronted rock樂團「 START OF THE DAY 」。 融合了後搖滾與瞪鞋搖滾,充滿漂浮感的樂章中, 搭配管弦與打擊樂器的經典音色,以及絕妙的和聲, 交織而成的音樂,猶如「搖滾交響樂團」。 他們所創作的音樂是獨一無二、投影在你心中的「愛」與「希望」。\n\nBiography\n2002年成團。\n受到90年代情緒搖滾濃厚色彩影響，START OF THE DAY的音樂創作就此開始。\n巡迴世界各國，參與許多大型戶外搖滾音樂祭演出，\n推出三張專輯與EP，一張個團DVD，多張的合輯與DVD作品。\n最新EP「THE BATON」在日本的最後一場專輯巡迴演出時，\n結合了現場和聲、管弦樂與打擊樂團、VJ影像等，\n表演人數動員15人的完美演出。\n表演現場，沸騰的氣氛中滿溢著歡喜，\n成為了一段傳奇的精彩演出。\n2013年，START OF THE DAY將以「THE BATON」的海外巡迴，\n與新的音樂制作，往未來繼續努力大步邁進。\n\nDiscography\n2003.11.18 1st mini album \\\\\\"I will stay as I am\\\\\\" \n2006.01.11 2nd mini album \\\\\\"from here to anywhere\\\\\\" \n2006.11.01 3rd mini album \\\\\\"Natural wave\\\\\\" \n2007.08.08 1st full album \\\\\\"Joy and Love , Pain and Hope\\\\\\"\n2008.11.12 2nd full album \\\\\\"Melody Runner\\\\\\"\n2009.09.16 1st Digital Single \\\\\\"One Long-lasting Belief\\\\\\"\n2010.10.21.best album \\\\\\"The Everlasting Days\\\\\\"\n2010.09.02 3rd Full Album \\\\\\"LOVE\\\\\\" in Taiwan\n2010.09.29 3rd Full Album \\\\\\"LOVE\\\\\\" in JAPAN\n2012.10.10 EP \\\\\\"THE BATON\\\\\\" in JAPAN'),
(75535, 'UN-TONED Experimental ', 'http://www.indievox.com/untoned', 'http://cdn-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/90000/75535/pix/75535180X180.jpg?1427792477', 71, 'about:\nUN-TONED studio\n\n\nFrom early took part in improvisational Jazz Heavy Egg Hell Dog (domed hell dogs) Huang Yirui (yellow animal), Tan Hanjun (Fei), Lai Guanlun and The Poisondwarf Ensemble of South Africa who Andre \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\'' and Berserker Lai started, the free music forms and experiment with various sounds at ease combined Cui unexpectedly pregnant UN-TONED the premise of refining and development of experimental Studio.\nStorm bucket prepared combination of tragedy or minor form of acting, we are trying to create is perhaps composers of avant-garde but there are rogue; find all sorts of music from rock and roll and blues image until it resembles the taste, receive from the Bebop jazz of Japan Japanese rock garden wind Jian Le. Un-is the combined interpretation of the whip hit the chord decomposition can also adopt different views accept infinite possibilities, for the love of music or relaxing or deep spectrum under each of the present.\n2010 UN-TONED Bassist jellyfish (Chen Yanting), fashion design, 070 (Lin Qiling), yellow mixed elite epic animal longings and ideals and quickly ran to the hope for a bright future.\n\nMain art design help (Zhang Yuling), Abra. Rita (You Huijing), finance expert Nomar (Jiang Boxuan) and three are both musical expertise or personal academic backgrounds are more UN-TONED sound more distinctive, have begun to undertake creative invitation!\nAt the same time gradually with each UN-TONED Studio will also be in the future creation of members of private, video media, such as fashion, music, art, paintings, literature, financing and export of complex and diverse UN-TONED design lebal!\n\n< Σ 嘆息伶人之e小調 悲歌編年史 >\n\n  從前期曾參與即興爵士Heavy Egg Hell Dog(巨蛋地獄狗)的黃亦睿(黃動物)、譚翰駿(飛鴻)、賴冠倫加上The Poisondwarf Ensemble的南非籍Andre’和Berserker L