(113003, 'kanina', 'http://www.indievox.com/kanina', 'http://cdn-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/120000/113003/pix/113003180X180.jpg?1427773239', 100, 'Kanina is a post-classical, ambient band hailing from Japan that weaves together musical performance and storytelling. Meaning \\"rabbit\\" in Icelandic, Kanina takes songs and turns them into chapters of a story. Digital programming, effects, piano, glockenspiel, and guitar come together to make Kanina\\''s unique sound. The effect is the creation of a vast, majestic world that evokes beauty and the fragility of nature. Seeking more than conventional sounds, they take their expression of music beyond traditional band forms. Yukino\\''s enchanting voice surrounds and softens the hearts of those listening while Kentaro paints delicate images on an ever-changing canvas.\r\n\r\n\\"A Short Story\\" is the tale of a little boy. \r\nHis journey is about to begin.'),
