(122319, '林郁容', 'http://www.indievox.com/linyurong99', 'http://cdn-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/150000/122319/pix/122319180X180.JPG?1427807821', 11, '小時在琴鍵上玩耍開始彈琴，所以彈琴就是純粹開心的事。 喜歡的旋律，就想辨法在琴鍵上玩出自己的感覺來。 小學後才開始學古典、練合唱，初中學流行爵士等，後來持續進修，考級學習等，並同時教大小朋友彈琴。 受到David Earl 老師的啟發和鼓勵，開始練習冥想並創作,平衡狀態下,自然而然地記錄下心靈流動出的樂音。 06年開始在網路上傳,希望我的音樂能和大家分享心靈感動,分享愛...'),
(122398, 'TAUN', 'http://www.indievox.com/taunband', 'http://cdn-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/150000/122398/pix/122398180X180.jpg?1427773447', 21, 'Taun was birthed through musical frustration and has evovled over the past eight years into an original expression of Rock eminating from an ecclectic blend of influences.  By harnessing both the melodic and dissonant riffs of Metal, incorporating the smooth 	and warm bass tones of RnB, expressing them via the heavy distorted crunch of Rock and encompassing them with strong male vocals; Taun is giving Rock a new flavour that is distinctly unique.\r\n\r\nInstigated initially by REAL in 2002 after a short stint at the Western Australian 	Academy of Perfroming Arts.  Real’s love for music was ingrained in him young, 	influenced by exposure to Led Zeplyn, Hendrix, The Cure, B-52s, Iron Maiden. Having a background of playing in Punk, Rock, Grunge, Speed Metal, Covers bands, \r\nScottish Pipe bands, Musical Productions, Rock n Roll, Reggae, Cumbia and Jazz.\r\n\r\nIn late 2010 REAL was joined by Scott ‘OAK’ Baggaley, initially on Bass and now on Lead Guitar.  OAK has been performing in Rock bands and Acoustically around Perth since he was at University, where he helped form the band Oak, recording the demo album The Blue Project and has also performed under the pseudonym SCOTT JAMES and self-recorded a demo album Left Behind.  With musical influences steming from U2, Pearl Jam and Live.\r\n\r\nAna Mac joined Taun in the earlier stages of its development more on a casual basis and now is an integral member of the team.  Combining her Managing experience, Promotion/Marketing and general love of music into the mix.  With experience in Covers bands, Gospel, Grunge, Musical Productions, Rock n Roll and RnB.\r\n\r\n'),
(122573, '原本不該是這樣', 'http://www.indievox.com/itisnotwhatithought', 'http://cdn1-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/150000/122573/pix/122573180X180.jpg?1427773451', 113, '在那之後，我想我失去了生命中某些重要的東西。\r\n很多時候我們總滿懷熱情，期待擁有和自己當初所想相符的結果。\r\n但事實卻常常與期待有所落差，我也不是沒有想過要做些什麼。\r\n在用盡心思拚了命之後，卻常常也只能低頭長嘆。\r\n無奈的處境，悲傷的結果，原本不該是這樣吧。\r\n又或者，其實是我們太年幼太天真，根本也沒有什麼好唉聲嘆氣的。\r\n\r\n成員\r\nVOCAL    李承昊(滾蛋)\r\nGUITAR  姚嘉凱\r\nBASS      姬野洋樹(HIRO)\r\nDRUMS  蔡杰倫(前獨立人種鼓手)\r\n\r\n無奈悲觀多愁善感的心理世界，請給我們一點安慰跟掌聲，因為我們怕孤單。\r\n原本，不該是這樣。\r\n\r\n<表演經歷>\r\n多次東海熱音社成果發表\r\n2011搖滾台中校際熱音賽\r\n迴響音樂藝文展演空間  12/15新聲搖滾-浴火鳳凰\r\n東海大學搖滾樂生命史及攝影回顧展\r\n2011東海大學聖誕\r\n豐樂公園2012年年新希望shopping節 愛心園遊會\r\n'),
