(150466, '宠物同谋', 'http://www.indievox.com/petconspiracy', 'http://cdn-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/180000/150466/pix/150466180X180.jpg?1427774067', 3, '宠物同谋乐队由虎子，Mary, Edo，晕晕组成。它将朋克摇滚和艺术项目相结合，宠物同谋以震撼的现场表演在国内外迅速蹿红——被评为“2009年当月优秀MTV乐队”和“2010中国最佳电子乐队”。宠物同谋在短短不到两年时间成为中国最炙手可热的原创乐队。2008年，宠物同谋在欧洲崭露头角，并在欧洲最酷的俱乐部表演，并由此获得了众多国际观众的热情和喜爱，欧洲各大媒体如，Arte TV, BBC还在International, Compilations等争相报道。\r\n在音乐方面，宠物同谋受到朋克摇滚，新浪潮和电子乐的影响。现场表演方面，乐队完美糅合了Peaches和Crystal Castle以及德国超现实电影的剧场气氛。\r\n与其说宠物同谋是一个乐队，不如把它当成是一个艺术项目更为贴切。看他们的现场演出不只是一次娱乐，而更多的是一次奇妙的体验。'),
(150478, 'Eatliz', 'http://www.indievox.com/eatliz', 'http://cdn2-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/180000/150478/pix/150478180X180.JPG?1427774067', 5, '以色列最炙手可热的艺术摇滚组合 Eatliz, 多年来在另类摇滚领域掀起一股风潮, 乐队的音乐异彩, 迅速横扫北美、欧洲和以色列, 成为新一代的摇滚酷派。 \r\nEatliz是以色列特拉维夫市內最具创意的乐团, 在世界各地的现场演出无不令人拍案叫绝, 新颖的跨流派音乐, 结合震撼的动画音乐录象, 使乐团在中国荣获众多奖项。\r\n乐团过去五年的专辑唱片广受好评, 钟情非传统编曲的乐迷, 纷纷成为其忠实信徒。乐团喜把持续的重击声和细腻曲折的视觉情节相混合, 为聆听体验赋予深刻的寓意。被冠以“艺术摇滚”的Eatliz, 从流行音乐、中东乐声和重型摇滚中取材, 缔造出全新的音乐神话, 令人不禁想起如Faith No More、The Cranberries和Blonde Redhead等创意音乐组合。\r\n\r\n\r\nTel Aviv`s hottest Art Rockers Eatliz have been causing quite a stir in the world of alternative rock for some time now, earning them an ever-growing cult following across North America, Europe and China bringing their spectacular high energy must see shows, outstanding genre-crossing music and cutting-edge awarded animated music videos, which earned the band a great deal of press attention worldwide, along with performances on TV shows and major music festivals. \r\n\r\nReleasing albums to critical acclaim, the band’s tendency for sonic pounding mixed with delicate twisting have struck a chord with listeners worldwide who appreciate unconventional song structure and intense roaring loudness meets playful mood swings. Playing what’s been termed as “Art Rock” Eatliz music features elements ranging from pop with a Middle Eastern edge to action packed  Bi-polar guitars with a a winning combination of melodic hooks. The result is a sound that calls to mind artists like Blonde Redhead, Bjork and Portishead. The variety of styles the band combines in a single song, has helped them gain fans of many genres, crossing ages and countries.\r\n\r\nEatliz astounding creative vision has gained a reputation for their eye-popping web sensations animation music videos for songs such as`Lose This Child`, `Hey` and “Attractive”, which were seen by millions in 200 festivals all over the world where they received dozens of awards, including the prestigious`Spike Lee Award` granted by the renowned director at the New York Tribeca Film Festival, plus screenings before the film `Avatar` at cinemas across America.\r\n\r\nConstantly on the road, Eatliz have been touring around the world showcasing their unique style to the masses, performing at major festivals as Primavera sound, Exit and SXSW including the slot of opening act for Porcupine Tree and `Zappa Plays Zappa`. Recently Eatliz finished an extensive headline tour across China, including sold out shows at JUE | Music + Art festival while getting wide press coverage and impressing major Chinese media as CCTV, Time Out Beijing and Painkiller magazine.\r\n\r\n``Known for their brand of grandiose art rock, the band undoubtedly impressed Hong Kong music lovers`` - Bitetone magazine Hong Kong\r\n\r\n``No matter how their sounds transform and evolve, there is always a lingering hint of darkness, a twist of black humour that lurks in the background of their music – a raw energy that Hong Kong will soon witness first hand`` - Time Out Hong Kong\r\n\r\n``This was the first time for me to see Eatliz live and they blew my mind`` - Misunderrated magazine Hong Kong\r\n\r\n``Eatliz makes dreamy, atmospheric songs and imbuing them with complex and ornate arrangements and haunting vocals``\r\nMTV Buzzworthy \r\n'),
(150507, 'Blockhead', 'http://www.indievox.com/blockhead', 'http://cdn1-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/180000/150507/pix/150507180X180.jpg?1427774068', 1, '◎懷念那個手機與網路出現以先，滿是張牙舞爪創意的年代\r\n◎曼哈頓地下嘻哈怪傑，個人第五張實驗大碟\r\n◎多色環境音效、迷濛合成取樣音色，呈現經典Blockhead聲韻\r\n'),
(150512, '虎子&王娟', 'http://www.indievox.com/huziandwangjuan', 'http://cdn-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/180000/150512/pix/150512180X180.jpg?1427774068', 0, '电子音乐人虎子和民谣歌手王娟的合作是折衷的，laptop加上民谣混成的沙发音乐，符合石榴厂牌的一贯路线，并没有太多新意，和两人此前各自的作品相比，在国内却反而迎来了更多的掌声。这张EP唱片更像是一次偶遇，而不是精心炮制的产物。 　　 　　\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n请用对待一张流行消费音乐的态度对待这张唱片，尤其不要刻意联想，不然，这张唱片也不会在推广chill out的石榴厂牌推出，badhead且不是更好的选择？ 　　 　　\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n躺沙发上，聊天吹水，是这张唱片适合播放的场合。'),
