(157462, 'Shimmer Riot', 'http://www.indievox.com/shimmerriot', 'http://cdn1-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/180000/157462/pix/157462180X180.jpg?1427774219', 31, '精巧的古典吉他技法與失序音牆交繪潛意識底下的日常奇境\n\nEP"蛙鳴蝉噪 Wordmeansendout"發行中，可至演出現場購買或填寫線上訂購單：\nhttp://goo.gl/B7iYbj\n\n小白兔唱片"蘿蔔四代"：\nhttp://shop.wwr.com.tw/cd/va/lobo4-va-wwr-cd\n\nFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/ShimmerRiot\nYoutube: https://www.youtube.com/user/ShimmerRiot\nSoundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/shimmer-riot\n'),
