(330948, '台客', 'http://www.indievox.com/mikebtw', 'http://cdn-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/360000/330948/pix/330948180X180.jpg?1427778124', 2, 'Tai-K are a Kaohsiung rock band featuring:\nFrankie Fang: Bass & vocals Mike B: Guitar & Vocals, JJ (Jain Jain Guo): Drums\n\nMike B: Guitar & Vocals Born in England, Mike B is a veteran musician who has been in bands since his early teens. Some of the groups he has been associated with are: Guillotine Smile On Impact The Sirkits Xoom Klub He has also had a successful solo career working with such musicians as Texas Jake (former slide guitarist with Hendrix), & blues legend Doc H, In Taiwan, Mike has had a solo career, performing on ICRT. He has also been a member of the Brickyard Special Guest Band as a bass player, as well as composer, guitarist & vocalist with Simple Extacy. He co-founded Tai-K in 2013 with bass player Frankie Fang.. \n\n麥克 B: 吉他&歌手\n自青少年時期即參與許多樂團及演出 麥克 B是為經驗極佳的音樂表演者 曾參與Guillotine Smile On Impact The Sirkits Xoom Klub 等樂團 在單飛生涯也曾與Texas Jake (Jimmy Hendrix前吉他手) 及 blues legend Doc H一同演出 在台灣 曾受邀於全國唯一國際電台ICRT音樂網表演 麥克 B有他專屬自己的演出機會使他獲得極大回響 並有無數為之成功的表現 一直以來 他同時也是高雄著名音樂餐廳”紅磚地窖”指定的貝斯手特別嘉賓 Simple Extacy是他另創之二人樂團 主要負責吉他彈奏 作曲及男主唱 他於2013年與Frankie Fang共創本土樂團 Tai-K \n\nFrankie Fang: Bass & Vocals Frankie Fang , from Taiwan, has played in various bands ( ElectroCute, later Electrocutioners; Liger Attack ; Try Try Look ) through the years and has played along side such performers as Paul Squires, Paul Squires and Seamas Manly. Since cofounding Tai-K she has been more creative and has been busy collaborating in song writing as well as singing lead on quite a few of Tai-K''s songs. Frankie Fang determines to infuse as much as Taiwanese element in song-presenting to win Taiwanese audience’s heart. \n\n飛輪器: 貝斯吉他 女主唱\n\n飛輪器近年來參與過的樂團有 ElectroCute (later Electrocutioners with Imran, JZ, Paul and Marlboro)(龐克風), Liger Attack (with Paul Squires, John Hammings, Greg Haxton, Nick Bogelin), Try Try Look (雷鬼風樂團)並有幸與音樂奇筢如Seamas Manly同台演奏 自加入台客 飛輪器開始為該團作貝斯編曲及所相關歌曲創作 也為台客創作適合台灣人欣賞的中文搖滾歌曲\n'),
