(335567, '鬼毛 (Kenneth Yang)', 'http://www.indievox.com/kennethyang', 'http://cdn1-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/360000/335567/pix/335567180X180.jpg?1427778231', 0, '鬼毛，台灣作曲家、編曲師、音樂製作人。\n曾參與及製作國內外多項廣告、電影配樂、遊戲配樂等，台灣金光布袋戲合作編曲師，音樂曲風多元，以磅礡大氣的好萊塢式樂風為大宗。\n鬼毛從小學時代便開始學習創作歌曲，以極具天賦的才華很快的躍身成為台灣近代罕見的鬼才編曲師。\nKenneth Yang is quickly making a name for himself as one of Taiwan''s most talented young composers. Ken began writing music after teaching himself to　play the guitar. \nWhat started as simple tunes quickly developed into complex and exciting compositions as Ken started using MIDI sequencing software to arrange his work.\nKen started his music composition since elementary span, with his prodigy of years of self-crafting experiences, Ken quickly find his position in the industry working on scoring for Pili''s Puppet Anime. \nHis style is very cinematic and incorporates symphonic orchestra.\nKen has worked on a wide variety of mediums and\ngenres. \nHe wrote the musical score for the award-winning short film, Cry 2,which was chosen to participate in the Cannes Film Festival. He also worked on the Malaysian Kung Fu Film, Fist of Dragon, Shaolin Crime File, Lords of Legend, as well as various animated productions, films, television programs,and games.\nKen is also currently working on several feature-film scores.'),
(335568, '葉伯 。UNCLE YEH', 'http://www.indievox.com/uncleyeh', 'http://cdn3-data.indievox.com/indievox_user/360000/335568/pix/335568180X180.JPG?1427778231', 0, '台灣音樂製作人\n參與多項國內外電影配樂 廣告配樂 音樂製作 \n擅長開發新音效與聲音, 融合電音元素與交響層次, 製作多元曲風.'),
